# Gemini API Configuration
# Get your API key from: https://ai.google.dev/
#
# Steps:
# 1. Visit https://ai.google.dev/
# 2. Click "Get API Key"
# 3. Create a new API key from Google Cloud Console
# 4. Paste it below (keep it secret!)
#
# WARNING: Never commit this file with actual keys to public repositories!

GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here
